        "subtitle": "Simulated 5G network dataset with metrics.",
        "description": "This project simulates a large-scale 5G network performance dataset using Python and pandas in Google Colab. It generates synthetic data for various real-world metrics like signal strength, speed, latency, jitter, battery levels, and user experience across different cities \u2014 with special focus on Indian metro areas like Mumbai, Chennai, Delhi, and Kolkata. The dataset includes detailed attributes like device model, carrier (Jio, Airtel, Vi), 5G frequency bands (n78, n28, n258), and environmental conditions. This data can be used for exploratory data analysis (EDA), network optimization modeling, predictive analytics, and machine learning experiments related to telecom service quality.\n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nThis project simulates a large-scale 5G network performance dataset using Python and pandas in Google Colab. It generates synthetic data for various real-world metrics like signal strength, speed, latency, jitter, battery levels, and user experience across different cities \u2014 with special focus on Indian metro areas like Mumbai, Chennai, Delhi, and Kolkata. The dataset includes detailed attributes like device model, carrier (Jio, Airtel, Vi), 5G frequency bands (n78, n28, n258), and environmental conditions. This data can be used for exploratory data analysis (EDA), network optimization modeling, predictive analytics, and machine learning experiments related to telecom service quality.\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\nTimestamp: Date and time when the measurement was taken (recorded every 10 minutes).\nLocation: City where the test was conducted (Indian and global cities).\nSignal Strength (dBm): Signal strength in decibels; values range from -110 (weak) to -60 (strong).\nDownload Speed (Mbps): [no description]\nUpload Speed (Mbps): [no description]\nLatency (ms): [no description]\nJitter (ms): [no description]\nNetwork Type: [no description]\nDevice Model: [no description]\nCarrier: [no description]\nBand: [no description]\nBattery Level (%): [no description]\nTemperature (\u00b0C): [no description]\nConnected Duration (min): [no description]\nHandover Count: [no description]\nData Usage (MB): [no description]\nVideo Streaming Quality: [no description]\nVoNR Enabled: [no description]\nNetwork Congestion Level: [no description]\nPing to Google (ms): [no description]\nDropped Connection: [no description]\n",
